title: Dallas Move Masters
body:
## Dallas move masters is a small but very much appreciated client. They allow us to stretch our creative legs and provide a stellar lockup for their business.

### ABOUT THE PROJECT

The Dallas Move Masters logo was a short but fulfilling project. We were on a tight budget and short deadline but we were able to deliver an outstanding mark for the client to use.
